    "Disposition": {
      "text": "If splinted and stabilized, can be discharged after consultation with Ortho\nAdmit for:\nOpen fracture\nSigns of neurovascular injury\nConcern for\ncompartment syndrome",
      "subsections": {
        "Specialty_Care": {
          "text": "Stable: short arm cast\nLong arm posterior splint\nwith 90 degrees of elbow flexion and the hand in a neutral position\nUnstable: ORIF\n>50% displacement\n>10% angulation\nInvolvement of proximal 1/3",
